WEBVTT

00:05.406 --> 00:08.474
<i> - (Sniffling)</i>

00:12.346 --> 00:14.446
(Car rumbles)

00:15.449 --> 00:17.716
(Crying)

00:21.088 --> 00:22.321
(Tires screech)

