08:17.831 --> 08:19.865
but...

08:22.236 --> 08:23.902
here you are.
- (Gasps)

08:24.004 --> 08:26.538
- Until I get a real diamond.

08:26.640 --> 08:29.241
- (Shocked laugh) Are you
asking me to marry you?

08:30.844 --> 08:32.711
- It's more of a promise.

08:32.813 --> 08:34.913
I don't wanna lose you.

08:35.015 --> 08:37.048
- But I'm not going anywhere.

08:37.150 --> 08:40.252
- Yeah, but you've got this
great job working at the salon

08:40.354 --> 08:42.821
and I don't want some other guy
to come by

08:42.923 --> 08:45.624
and scoop you up.

08:45.726 --> 08:47.225
- I wouldn't do that.

08:47.327 --> 08:49.995
I'm happy with you.

08:50.097 --> 08:53.031
- And I wanna keep it that way.

08:53.133 --> 08:55.967
I want you, Lorena,

08:58.639 --> 09:01.306
