09:04.278 --> 09:05.844
I love you.

09:07.881 --> 09:09.414
- I love you, too.

09:15.989 --> 09:17.522
(Giggles happily)

09:19.126 --> 09:21.860
<i>Lorena: I built fantasies of us</i>
<i> spending our lives together,</i>

09:21.962 --> 09:24.129
<i> living around the world,</i>

09:24.231 --> 09:26.131
