for a couple of weeks.

11:10.537 --> 11:12.537
- Well, John says a lot
of things.

11:14.041 --> 11:15.273
What do you say?

11:17.811 --> 11:20.612
- Maybe we'll go on
a double date?

11:20.714 --> 11:22.247
- (Chuckles)

