13:06.520 --> 13:08.553
- I'm hungry,
and this is no fun.

13:08.655 --> 13:10.288
- I dunno, Todd and I are
having a blast.

13:10.390 --> 13:11.756
- Two.

13:13.160 --> 13:15.326
- Okay, fine. You two stay
and take a cab home.

13:15.428 --> 13:17.529
