You're going to get us killed.

13:53.300 --> 13:56.000
- Shut up!
I know what I'm doing!

13:56.102 --> 13:57.402
(Car horn blares)
- Ahhhhh!

13:57.504 --> 13:59.237
(Tires squeal)

13:59.339 --> 14:02.774
