- Don't ever do that again!

14:02.876 --> 14:04.542
- (Gasping for breath)

14:04.644 --> 14:06.344
(Crying) You were in
the other lane.

14:08.048 --> 14:09.747
(Hard punch, Lorena screams)
- What the hell do you know?

14:09.850 --> 14:11.482
