to put up um...

15:17.684 --> 15:19.684
the... (laughs)
put up the curtains yet.

15:19.786 --> 15:21.019
- Okay.

15:23.223 --> 15:24.656
What about the fight?

15:27.894 --> 15:29.928
- Oh!

15:30.030 --> 15:32.163
Oh...

15:32.265 --> 15:33.998
It's not like that.

