1:02:07.624 --> 1:02:09.057
- What the hell is this?

1:02:11.195 --> 1:02:12.728
- It's mine, John. Don't--

1:02:12.830 --> 1:02:15.530
(Struggling grunts,
recorder rewinds)

1:02:17.067 --> 1:02:18.533
<i> John's voice: You will be</i>
<i> nothing without me, right?!</i>

1:02:18.635 --> 1:02:19.868
- Why the hell are you
recording me?

1:02:19.970 --> 1:02:22.604
<i> Recording: ...a worthless,</i>
<i> stupid--</i>

1:02:22.706 --> 1:02:25.974
- No! No!
- Answer me!

1:02:26.076 --> 1:02:27.476
(Door opens)
- Dude, hurry up

1:02:27.578 --> 1:02:29.411
or we're gonna miss Happy Hour!

1:02:29.513 --> 1:02:31.379
- Just saying goodbye to wifey.

1:02:33.851 --> 1:02:35.717
<i> (Door closes)</i>

1:02:35.819 --> 1:02:37.319
- (Whimpers and gasps)

1:02:38.589 --> 1:02:39.955
- (Menacingly) You're gonna pay
for this later.

1:02:40.057 --> 1:02:42.624
(Hard smack,
Lorena cries out)

1:02:44.528 --> 1:02:45.794
(Normal tone) Let's go.

1:02:46.830 --> 1:02:48.830
(Door closes)

1:02:48.932 --> 1:02:51.466
- (Sobbing)

1:02:58.275 --> 1:03:00.108
