1:04:13.784 --> 1:04:15.517
(Deep, shaky breath)

1:04:18.222 --> 1:04:21.790
He um...

1:04:21.892 --> 1:04:23.291
he kick me,

1:04:25.629 --> 1:04:27.195
he punch me,

1:04:28.398 --> 1:04:29.898
and he...

1:04:32.135 --> 1:04:34.402
