1:04:36.974 --> 1:04:38.540
and then...

1:04:40.544 --> 1:04:43.044
the, the sex.

1:04:43.146 --> 1:04:44.446
- Excuse me?

1:04:46.516 --> 1:04:48.316
- Sex. He, he...

1:04:48.418 --> 1:04:50.485
he, he make me

1:04:50.587 --> 1:04:52.754
when I don't want to.

1:04:52.856 --> 1:04:55.690
