1:05:18.448 --> 1:05:20.949
- If you want to file this
petition, you do.

1:05:21.051 --> 1:05:23.084
She gets back at one.

1:05:23.186 --> 1:05:24.819
- I... I can't do that.

1:05:24.922 --> 1:05:25.287
My job...

1:05:26.857 --> 1:05:28.290
- What about after work?

1:05:29.760 --> 1:05:31.493
- I have to go home.

